# No environment variables are required for the Dataverse data layer.
#
# The app talks to Dataverse through the Microsoft Dataverse *connector* using
# the connection's "current environment" — so a single build/solution targets
# whichever environment it is deployed/promoted into (dev → QA → prod)
# automatically. There is no org URL to configure.
#
# (Historical note: VITE_DATAVERSE_ORG_URL used to bake a single org URL into
# the bundle at build time, which broke one-artifact promotion. It is no longer
# read by the app.)
